  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effects of three interventions on CPAP adherence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether there is a need for a more intensive one on one interaction with the
      patient in order to improve CPAP usage. And also to try to identify in general which
      population of patients may require a more intensive intervention.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
